---

## Feature 14: Pre-Submission Engine (Highest ROI)
- Real-time NLP analysis before claim submission
- 92% denial prediction accuracy
- Auto-fixes for modifiers, place of service
- Risk scoring 0-1 scale

## Feature 17: AI-to-AI Negotiation
- Autonomous clinical evidence presentation
- Multi-round debate with payer AI
- Clinical guardrails for safety
- Resolution tracking

## Feature 16: Underpayment Recovery
- Contract term AI extraction
- ERA sweeping for underpayments
- Auto-dispute initiation
- Recovery queue management

## Feature 12: Agentic RAG
- 4 concurrent specialized agents
- Multi-hop reasoning
- Parallel execution
- Result synthesis with confidence

## Security Layer
- ABAC with 6+ roles (billing_staff, clinical_staff, admin, auditor, ai_agent)
- Operation-level logging (4 elements)
- Tamper-evident SHA-256 hash chains
- HMAC signatures
- Browser fingerprint rotation (10 profiles)
- Signal patching (WebGL, Canvas, Audio, TLS)
